    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《 <strong><i>Bean There, Swung That</i></strong> 》是一款基于动量通过抓钩摆动来运动的快节奏3D游戏。荡过形形色色的关卡、收集检查点、避免致命碰撞，熟练使用抓钩，以最快速度冲向终点。你可以选择单人挑战，也可以在在线多人模式中与最多 10 位好友同台竞速。记住，在分秒必争的同时要步步为营，每一次的摆动都至关重要。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321060/extras/670d8a255954a7944a2a8b275ef67211.poster.avif?t=1764371387\" width=480 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321060/extras/670d8a255954a7944a2a8b275ef67211.webm?t=1764371387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321060/extras/670d8a255954a7944a2a8b275ef67211.mp4?t=1764371387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏特色：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快节奏，无速度上限——你的技巧决定了你的上限。别撞上任何东西，几乎所有碰撞都会导致失败。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321060/extras/1ff2b2d82c076fa339de235c3314896f.poster.avif?t=1764371387\" width=480 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321060/extras/1ff2b2d82c076fa339de235c3314896f.webm?t=1764371387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321060/extras/1ff2b2d82c076fa339de235c3314896f.mp4?t=1764371387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >争夺奖牌，挑战游戏开发者的时间记录并超越自我。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在线游戏大厅中最多可支持 10 人同台竞速。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 5 个不同主题中，包含了90 个手工打造独具特色的关卡——专为速度与技巧所设计。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321060/extras/d6508b2114815f5a349f41d49cb02020.poster.avif?t=1764371387\" width=480 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321060/extras/d6508b2114815f5a349f41d49cb02020.webm?t=1764371387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321060/extras/d6508b2114815f5a349f41d49cb02020.mp4?t=1764371387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁皮肤、拖尾和钩索，自定义你的外观风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索独属于你的路线。每个关卡都为拥有多条路径的障碍赛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑战高难度专家关卡，超越你的极限。</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 日语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 俄语, 简体中文, 土耳其语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
